      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is exceedingly rare. This is an investment-grade example, meticulously maintained to ensure it meets the exacting requirements of the most discerning collector. Experience an uncompromising level of refinement and mechanical integrity in a vehicle that presents as if it just departed the factory floor.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
