    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true time-capsule vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory shine with zero stone chips or imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple with no creasing, and every control operates with crisp, factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with only genuine parts used. It drives as tightly as the day it left the showroom floor. Included are all original manuals, two master keys, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to own a benchmark example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
