    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber, maintained to exacting showroom standards. This vehicle occupies a rare tier of preservation, exhibiting an interior and exterior entirely free of compromise. Meticulously curated and mechanically superlative, it represents a definitive acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing short of excellence. We invite you to inspect this flawlessly presented example of engineering integrity.",
