      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm so excited for whoever gets to take this home! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
